{"tid":2047932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟限聚令係去到6月18定8月31？","createTime":"2020-06-02T12:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T12:51:53.000Z","uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3f259a5ce6308ba94dec3f0be4d0c0dfa4c178","tid":2047932,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"食物及衛生局長陳肇始表示，考慮最新疫情後，行政會議決定將限制食肆處所營業及限制聚集的規例有效期，延長兩個月至8月31日，因應現時疫情，兩條規例現行的限制，會在6月4日到期後再延長14日至本月18日，有需要時可以再收緊。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始又指，新型冠狀病毒預計在未來一段時間會繼續存在，防疫工作需要納入社會運作成為新常態，亦預期未來社區可能出現零星本地個案或小型爆發，政府會繼續採取張弛有度的策略，保障公共衛生及平衡經濟影響及社會接受程度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1297561&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1297561%26csid%3D261_341&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=a8afb611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1297561&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"2398c73eceb2525c4bfa8d41efc8288c6f987e37","tid":2047932,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"睇顏色架姐"},{"pid":"270c13f7be622b946e81f629b497746eea29496e","tid":2047932,"uid":40716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"第599F同599G章嘅權力到8月31 而家限聚令到6月18<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ecdfa5736739de9211b2a66c95f96538cd6f43a","tid":2047932,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"2047既6月30"},{"pid":"232cc41e1a7ac32737ec46dc03e30c3dfe3c650d","tid":2047932,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"直到永遠，阿門"}]}